.com/2023/9/15/23873988/tiktok-eu-ireland-privacy -fine-childrens-data&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/15/23873988/tiktok-eu-ireland-privacy-fine-childrens-data" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/15/23873988/tiktok-eu-ireland-privacy-fine-childrens-data</id><author><name>佐藤米娅</name></author></entry></feed>